data.name: layChkHyujin.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT 'Y' FROM DUAL WHERE EXISTS ( SELECT 'Y' FROM OUT1001 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.RESER_YN = 'Y' AND A.NAEWON_DATE BETWEEN TO_DATE(:f_start_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AND TO_DATE(:f_end_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') AND A.DOCTOR IN ( SELECT B.DOCTOR FROM BAS0270 B WHERE B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND NVL(B.TONGGYE_DOCTOR,B.DOCTOR) = :f_doctor AND TO_DATE(:f_start_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD') BETWEEN B.START_DATE AND B.END_DATE ))
